"8PT1132M.1A1G", "PT1132M", and "REV-A1" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. {{See also|D-Link DCS-933L rev A2|List of Camera Devices}}
Despite using RT3352 in the FCC internal photos, this device is limited to single-stream operation. :An additional model of DCS-5010L is noted as sharing this FCC ID in the test report. Default credentials are per the FCC manual.
